###  http://www.semanticweb.org/94180/ontologies/2023/3/untitled-ontology-8/Clay_cementation_test
<http://www.semanticweb.org/94180/ontologies/2023/3/untitled-ontology-8/Clay_cementation_test> rdf:type owl:Class ;
