                                                                                                           owl:onProperty <http://www.semanticweb.org/94180/ontologies/2023/3/untitled-ontology-8/requiredParameters> ;
                                                                                                           owl:someValuesFrom <http://www.semanticweb.org/94180/ontologies/2023/3/untitled-ontology-8/Groundwater_parameters>
                                                                                                         ] ,
                                                                                                         [ rdf:type owl:Restriction ;
                                                                                                           owl:onProperty <http://www.semanticweb.org/94180/ontologies/2023/3/untitled-ontology-8/requiredParameters> ;
                                                                                                           owl:someValuesFrom <http://www.semanticweb.org/94180/ontologies/2023/3/untitled-ontology-8/Historical_landslide_data>
                                                                                                         ] ,
                                                                                                         [ rdf:type owl:Restriction ;
                                                                                                           owl:onProperty <http://www.semanticweb.org/94180/ontologies/2023/3/untitled-ontology-8/requiredParameters> ;
                                                                                                           owl:someValuesFrom <http://www.semanticweb.org/94180/ontologies/2023/3/untitled-ontology-8/Internal_friction_angle>
                                                                                                         ] ,
                                                                                                         [ rdf:type owl:Restriction ;
                                                                                                           owl:onProperty <http://www.semanticweb.org/94180/ontologies/2023/3/untitled-ontology-8/requiredParameters> ;
                                                                                                           owl:someValuesFrom <http://www.semanticweb.org/94180/ontologies/2023/3/untitled-ontology-8/Rainfall_parameters>
                                                                                                         ] ,
                                                                                                         [ rdf:type owl:Restriction ;
                                                                                                           owl:onProperty <http://www.semanticweb.org/94180/ontologies/2023/3/untitled-ontology-8/requiredParameters> ;
                                                                                                           owl:someValuesFrom <http://www.semanticweb.org/94180/ontologies/2023/3/untitled-ontology-8/Vegetation_parameters>
                                                                                                         ] ,
                                                                                                         [ rdf:type owl:Restriction ;
                                                                                                           owl:onProperty <http://www.semanticweb.org/94180/ontologies/2023/3/untitled-ontology-8/requiredParameters> ;
                                                                                                           owl:someValuesFrom <http://www.semanticweb.org/94180/ontologies/2023/3/untitled-ontology-8/Slope,_aspect,_elevation>
                                                                                                         ] ;
                                                                                         <http://www.semanticweb.org/94180/ontologies/2023/3/untitled-ontology-8/comment> """In the study of landslide slope mechanics, some empirical models are also widely used to estimate the strength and deformation characteristics of soils. These models are usually based on field surveys and test results to provide an approximate description of soil behavior in the form of empirical formulas
Rainfall characteristic parameters: including rainfall amount, rain intensity, rain time and rain pattern, etc. These parameters can be obtained from meteorological observations and can also be estimated from historical rainfall records and meteorological data.

Terrain feature parameters: Include slope, aspect, terrain undulation, and so on. These parameters can be obtained from topographic survey data, digital elevation models (DEMs) or satellite remote sensing images, for example.

Soil characteristic parameters: including soil type, particle distribution, water content, etc. These parameters can be obtained through in-situ surveys, laboratory tests, or existing soil databases and geological maps.

Vegetation cover parameters: including vegetation type, coverage, root characteristics, etc. These parameters can be obtained through vegetation surveys, remote sensing image interpretation, or related literature.

Historical landslide data: including the location, scale, impact, etc. of historical landslides. These data can be obtained through historical records, satellite remote sensing imagery or relevant disaster reports and documentation.

Groundwater conditions: including groundwater level, hydrological conditions, etc. These parameters can be obtained from hydrological observations, hydrological surveys or associated hydrological data.""" .


