                                                                                                                            ] ,
                                                                                                                            [ rdf:type owl:Restriction ;
                                                                                                                              owl:onProperty <http://www.semanticweb.org/94180/ontologies/2023/3/untitled-ontology-8/requiredParameters> ;
                                                                                                                              owl:someValuesFrom <http://www.semanticweb.org/94180/ontologies/2023/3/untitled-ontology-8/Elastic_modulus>
                                                                                                                            ] ,
                                                                                                                            [ rdf:type owl:Restriction ;
                                                                                                                              owl:onProperty <http://www.semanticweb.org/94180/ontologies/2023/3/untitled-ontology-8/requiredParameters> ;
                                                                                                                              owl:someValuesFrom <http://www.semanticweb.org/94180/ontologies/2023/3/untitled-ontology-8/Internal_friction_angle>
                                                                                                                            ] ,
                                                                                                                            [ rdf:type owl:Restriction ;
                                                                                                                              owl:onProperty <http://www.semanticweb.org/94180/ontologies/2023/3/untitled-ontology-8/requiredParameters> ;
                                                                                                                              owl:someValuesFrom <http://www.semanticweb.org/94180/ontologies/2023/3/untitled-ontology-8/Material_parameters>
                                                                                                                            ] ,
                                                                                                                            [ rdf:type owl:Restriction ;
                                                                                                                              owl:onProperty <http://www.semanticweb.org/94180/ontologies/2023/3/untitled-ontology-8/requiredParameters> ;
                                                                                                                              owl:someValuesFrom <http://www.semanticweb.org/94180/ontologies/2023/3/untitled-ontology-8/Permeability>
                                                                                                                            ] ,
                                                                                                                            [ rdf:type owl:Restriction ;
                                                                                                                              owl:onProperty <http://www.semanticweb.org/94180/ontologies/2023/3/untitled-ontology-8/requiredParameters> ;
                                                                                                                              owl:someValuesFrom <http://www.semanticweb.org/94180/ontologies/2023/3/untitled-ontology-8/Permeability_coefficient>
                                                                                                                            ] ,
                                                                                                                            [ rdf:type owl:Restriction ;
                                                                                                                              owl:onProperty <http://www.semanticweb.org/94180/ontologies/2023/3/untitled-ontology-8/requiredParameters> ;
                                                                                                                              owl:someValuesFrom <http://www.semanticweb.org/94180/ontologies/2023/3/untitled-ontology-8/Shear_modulus>
                                                                                                                            ] ,
                                                                                                                            [ rdf:type owl:Restriction ;
                                                                                                                              owl:onProperty <http://www.semanticweb.org/94180/ontologies/2023/3/untitled-ontology-8/requiredParameters> ;
                                                                                                                              owl:someValuesFrom <http://www.semanticweb.org/94180/ontologies/2023/3/untitled-ontology-8/Shear_strength>
                                                                                                                            ] ,
                                                                                                                            [ rdf:type owl:Restriction ;
                                                                                                                              owl:onProperty <http://www.semanticweb.org/94180/ontologies/2023/3/untitled-ontology-8/requiredParameters> ;
                                                                                                                              owl:someValuesFrom <http://www.semanticweb.org/94180/ontologies/2023/3/untitled-ontology-8/Poisson's_ratio>
                                                                                                                            ] ,
                                                                                                                            [ rdf:type owl:Restriction ;
                                                                                                                              owl:onProperty <http://www.semanticweb.org/94180/ontologies/2023/3/untitled-ontology-8/requiredParameters> ;
                                                                                                                              owl:someValuesFrom <http://www.semanticweb.org/94180/ontologies/2023/3/untitled-ontology-8/Slope,_aspect,_elevation>
                                                                                                                            ] ;
                                                                                                            <http://www.semanticweb.org/94180/ontologies/2023/3/untitled-ontology-8/comment> "A physical model for simulating the bearing behavior of pile foundations and underground structures. These models can be used to evaluate the stability and load transfer performance of the pile foundation by simulating geotechnical conditions." ;
                                                                                                            <http://www.semanticweb.org/94180/ontologies/2023/3/untitled-ontology-8/principle_of_the_model> """1. Model preparation: In the geotechnical pile foundation model experiment, it is first necessary to prepare the model according to the scale and geometry of the actual project. A scaled model is often used, i.e., the actual situation is scaled down to the appropriate scale for it to be carried out in the laboratory. Model preparation includes the selection of suitable materials, such as soil, piles, etc., and the accumulation or installation according to the design requirements.
2. Loading condition simulation: In the geotechnical pile foundation model experiment, the loading situation in the actual project is simulated by applying suitable load conditions. Vertical loads, horizontal loads, inclined loads, etc., can be applied to simulate different forces during the landslide. At the same time, the role of external forces such as simulated earthquakes and lateral groundwater pressure can also be considered.
3. Instrument monitoring and data acquisition: During the experiment, the displacement, stress, strain and other parameters of the soil and pile foundation in the model are recorded and monitored in real time through the instrument monitoring and data acquisition system. This data can be used for subsequent analysis and research.
4. Analysis and evaluation of the results: According to the experimental data, the results of the geotechnical pile foundation model can be analyzed and evaluated. Through the interpretation of displacement, stress distribution and other data, we can understand the interaction between soil and pile foundation in the process of landslide, as well as the mechanism of pile foundation in preventing landslide.""" .


