###  http://www.semanticweb.org/94180/ontologies/2023/3/untitled-ontology-8/Meso-macroscopic_coupling_model
<http://www.semanticweb.org/94180/ontologies/2023/3/untitled-ontology-8/Meso-macroscopic_coupling_model> rdf:type owl:Class ;
                                                                                                         rdfs:subClassOf <http://www.semanticweb.org/94180/ontologies/2023/3/untitled-ontology-8/Constitutive_model> ,
                                                                                                                         [ rdf:type owl:Restriction ;
                                                                                                                           owl:onProperty <http://www.semanticweb.org/94180/ontologies/2023/3/untitled-ontology-8/requiredParameters> ;
                                                                                                                           owl:someValuesFrom <http://www.semanticweb.org/94180/ontologies/2023/3/untitled-ontology-8/Cohesion>
                                                                                                                         ] ,
                                                                                                                         [ rdf:type owl:Restriction ;
                                                                                                                           owl:onProperty <http://www.semanticweb.org/94180/ontologies/2023/3/untitled-ontology-8/requiredParameters> ;
                                                                                                                           owl:someValuesFrom <http://www.semanticweb.org/94180/ontologies/2023/3/untitled-ontology-8/Compressive_strength>
                                                                                                                         ] ,
                                                                                                                         [ rdf:type owl:Restriction ;
                                                                                                                           owl:onProperty <http://www.semanticweb.org/94180/ontologies/2023/3/untitled-ontology-8/requiredParameters> ;
                                                                                                                           owl:someValuesFrom <http://www.semanticweb.org/94180/ontologies/2023/3/untitled-ontology-8/Elastic_modulus>
                                                                                                                         ] ,
                                                                                                                         [ rdf:type owl:Restriction ;
                                                                                                                           owl:onProperty <http://www.semanticweb.org/94180/ontologies/2023/3/untitled-ontology-8/requiredParameters> ;
                                                                                                                           owl:someValuesFrom <http://www.semanticweb.org/94180/ontologies/2023/3/untitled-ontology-8/Internal_friction_angle>
                                                                                                                         ] ,
                                                                                                                         [ rdf:type owl:Restriction ;
                                                                                                                           owl:onProperty <http://www.semanticweb.org/94180/ontologies/2023/3/untitled-ontology-8/requiredParameters> ;
                                                                                                                           owl:someValuesFrom <http://www.semanticweb.org/94180/ontologies/2023/3/untitled-ontology-8/Material_parameters>
                                                                                                                         ] ,
                                                                                                                         [ rdf:type owl:Restriction ;
                                                                                                                           owl:onProperty <http://www.semanticweb.org/94180/ontologies/2023/3/untitled-ontology-8/requiredParameters> ;
                                                                                                                           owl:someValuesFrom <http://www.semanticweb.org/94180/ontologies/2023/3/untitled-ontology-8/Permeability>
                                                                                                                         ] ,
                                                                                                                         [ rdf:type owl:Restriction ;
                                                                                                                           owl:onProperty <http://www.semanticweb.org/94180/ontologies/2023/3/untitled-ontology-8/requiredParameters> ;
                                                                                                                           owl:someValuesFrom <http://www.semanticweb.org/94180/ontologies/2023/3/untitled-ontology-8/Permeability_coefficient>
                                                                                                                         ] ,
                                                                                                                         [ rdf:type owl:Restriction ;
                                                                                                                           owl:onProperty <http://www.semanticweb.org/94180/ontologies/2023/3/untitled-ontology-8/requiredParameters> ;
                                                                                                                           owl:someValuesFrom <http://www.semanticweb.org/94180/ontologies/2023/3/untitled-ontology-8/Pore_water_pressure>
                                                                                                                         ] ;
                                                                                                         <http://www.semanticweb.org/94180/ontologies/2023/3/untitled-ontology-8/comment> "A constitutive model that combines the microstructure and macromechanical behavior of geotechnical materials is used to more accurately simulate the mechanical properties and deformation characteristics of slopes." ;
                                                                                                         <http://www.semanticweb.org/94180/ontologies/2023/3/untitled-ontology-8/principle_of_the_model> """1. Multi-scale modeling: The meso-macro coupling model takes into account physical processes at both the mesoscale and macroscale levels. At the mesoscale scale, the mesoscopic constitutive model is used to describe the microscopic behavior of soil particles, and at the macroscopic scale, the macroscopic constitutive model is used to describe the macroscopic mechanical response of soil.
2. Coupling method: The meso-macroscopic coupling model correlates the meso-macro-scale calculation results with each other through the coupling method. Techniques such as interface element or sub-region methods are often used to establish corresponding coupling relationships between mesoscale and macroscopic scale. This preserves the details of the mesoscale while taking into account the overall mechanical behavior at the macroscale.
3. Parameter transfer and correction: The meso-macro coupling model needs to transfer and correct the parameters at the meso-macro scale. At the meso-scale, particle-level material parameters are obtained through laboratory experiments or numerical simulations, and then these parameters are transferred to the macroscale by interfacial element or sub-region methods to obtain the parameters of the macroscopic constitutive model. At the same time, the mesoscale model is calibrated and modified according to the response results on the macroscopic scale.""" .


###  http://www.semanticweb.org/94180/ontologies/2023/3/untitled-ontology-8/Mesoscopic_constitutive_model
<http://www.semanticweb.org/94180/ontologies/2023/3/untitled-ontology-8/Mesoscopic_constitutive_model> rdf:type owl:Class ;
                                                                                                       rdfs:subClassOf <http://www.semanticweb.org/94180/ontologies/2023/3/untitled-ontology-8/Constitutive_model> ,
                                                                                                                       [ rdf:type owl:Restriction ;
                                                                                                                         owl:onProperty <http://www.semanticweb.org/94180/ontologies/2023/3/untitled-ontology-8/requiredParameters> ;
                                                                                                                         owl:someValuesFrom <http://www.semanticweb.org/94180/ontologies/2023/3/untitled-ontology-8/Elastic_modulus>
                                                                                                                       ] ,
                                                                                                                       [ rdf:type owl:Restriction ;
                                                                                                                         owl:onProperty <http://www.semanticweb.org/94180/ontologies/2023/3/untitled-ontology-8/requiredParameters> ;
                                                                                                                         owl:someValuesFrom <http://www.semanticweb.org/94180/ontologies/2023/3/untitled-ontology-8/Material_parameters>
                                                                                                                       ] ,
                                                                                                                       [ rdf:type owl:Restriction ;
                                                                                                                         owl:onProperty <http://www.semanticweb.org/94180/ontologies/2023/3/untitled-ontology-8/requiredParameters> ;
                                                                                                                         owl:someValuesFrom <http://www.semanticweb.org/94180/ontologies/2023/3/untitled-ontology-8/Permeability>
                                                                                                                       ] ,
                                                                                                                       [ rdf:type owl:Restriction ;
                                                                                                                         owl:onProperty <http://www.semanticweb.org/94180/ontologies/2023/3/untitled-ontology-8/requiredParameters> ;
                                                                                                                         owl:someValuesFrom <http://www.semanticweb.org/94180/ontologies/2023/3/untitled-ontology-8/Permeability_coefficient>
                                                                                                                       ] ,
                                                                                                                       [ rdf:type owl:Restriction ;
                                                                                                                         owl:onProperty <http://www.semanticweb.org/94180/ontologies/2023/3/untitled-ontology-8/requiredParameters> ;
                                                                                                                         owl:someValuesFrom <http://www.semanticweb.org/94180/ontologies/2023/3/untitled-ontology-8/Shear_modulus>
                                                                                                                       ] ,
                                                                                                                       [ rdf:type owl:Restriction ;
                                                                                                                         owl:onProperty <http://www.semanticweb.org/94180/ontologies/2023/3/untitled-ontology-8/requiredParameters> ;
                                                                                                                         owl:someValuesFrom <http://www.semanticweb.org/94180/ontologies/2023/3/untitled-ontology-8/Shear_strength>
                                                                                                                       ] ,
                                                                                                                       [ rdf:type owl:Restriction ;
                                                                                                                         owl:onProperty <http://www.semanticweb.org/94180/ontologies/2023/3/untitled-ontology-8/requiredParameters> ;
                                                                                                                         owl:someValuesFrom <http://www.semanticweb.org/94180/ontologies/2023/3/untitled-ontology-8/Poisson's_ratio>
                                                                                                                       ] ;
                                                                                                       <http://www.semanticweb.org/94180/ontologies/2023/3/untitled-ontology-8/comment> "The mesoscopic constitutive model attempts to describe the macroscopic mechanical behavior of the soil by considering the interaction between soil particles from the microstructure of the soil, such as the discrete element model and the finite element model." ;
                                                                                                       <http://www.semanticweb.org/94180/ontologies/2023/3/untitled-ontology-8/principle_of_the_model> """1. Particle-scale simulation: The mesoscopic constitutive model treats the soil as a discrete medium composed of many particles, and describes the mechanical behavior of the soil by simulating the interaction between the particles. Each particle is seen as a separate entity in the model, with mass, shape, and mechanical properties.
2. Particle-to-particle interactions: The mesoscopic constitutive model takes into account the contact and friction forces between the particles, as well as the mechanical behaviors such as cohesive forces that may exist. These interaction forces can be described by mechanical formulations or empirical relationships, often expressed using a spring-damping model or a contact force model.
3. Equation of Motion of Particles: The mesoscopic constitutive model is based on Newton's laws and simulates the mechanical response of the soil by solving the equations of motion of the particles. These equations take into account factors such as mass, inertial forces, external forces, and interaction forces, and can be solved by numerical methods such as the discrete element method.
4. Model parameters: The parameters of the mesoscopic constitutive model include the mass, shape, material properties of the particles, and the parameters of the interaction force model. These parameters need to be determined by laboratory experiments or particle-scale simulations to enable the model to accurately describe the micromechanical behavior of the soil.""" .


