###  http://www.semanticweb.org/94180/ontologies/2023/3/untitled-ontology-8/Soil_trough_model
<http://www.semanticweb.org/94180/ontologies/2023/3/untitled-ontology-8/Soil_trough_model> rdf:type owl:Class ;
