                                                                                                                 ] ;
                                                                                                 <http://www.semanticweb.org/94180/ontologies/2023/3/untitled-ontology-8/comment> """Stratigraphic rock type
	Clastic rock construction 34.7% pole
		Granular rocks such as sandstone, mudstone and conglomerate
	Magma rock builds 21.4% high
		Granite, andesite, basalt and other magma made of hard rock
	Metamorphic rock construction 21.7% high
		Gneiss, mica schist, mica-like schist, quartz schist, phyllite, shale and chlorite rock, etc
	Carbonate rock construction 19% medium
		Limestone, dolomite rock, calcareous rock, calcite rock, etc""" .


