                                                                                                                                                                                      "Tensile Test: The tensile test is used to determine the tensile strength and elastic modulus of metallic materials, fibrous materials, etc. In tensile tests, information about the modulus of elasticity can be obtained by applying a tensile load and recording the deformations and stresses of the material." ;
