                                                                                                    rdfs:subClassOf <http://www.semanticweb.org/94180/ontologies/2023/3/untitled-ontology-8/Permeability> ,
                                                                                                                    <http://www.semanticweb.org/94180/ontologies/2023/3/untitled-ontology-8/Permeability_coefficient> ,
                                                                                                                    <http://www.semanticweb.org/94180/ontologies/2023/3/untitled-ontology-8/Pore_water_pressure> ;
                                                                                                    <http://www.semanticweb.org/94180/ontologies/2023/3/untitled-ontology-8/principle_of_the_model> "Water injection experiment: By injecting water into a rock sample and monitoring the change in the pressure and permeability rate of the pore water, information about permeability is obtained." ,
                                                                                                                                                                                                    "Water injection experiment: By injecting water into a rock sample and monitoring the pressure changes of the pore water, the pressure response of the pore water under different conditions can be understood." ,
                                                                                                                                                                                                    "Water injection experiment: The permeability coefficient can be calculated by injecting water into a rock sample and monitoring changes in pore water pressure and permeability rate." .


