###  http://www.semanticweb.org/94180/ontologies/2023/3/untitled-ontology-8/Wind_tunnel_model
<http://www.semanticweb.org/94180/ontologies/2023/3/untitled-ontology-8/Wind_tunnel_model> rdf:type owl:Class ;
                                                                                           rdfs:subClassOf <http://www.semanticweb.org/94180/ontologies/2023/3/untitled-ontology-8/Physical_model> ,
                                                                                                           [ rdf:type owl:Restriction ;
                                                                                                             owl:onProperty <http://www.semanticweb.org/94180/ontologies/2023/3/untitled-ontology-8/requiredParameters> ;
                                                                                                             owl:someValuesFrom <http://www.semanticweb.org/94180/ontologies/2023/3/untitled-ontology-8/Boundary_parameters>
                                                                                                           ] ,
                                                                                                           [ rdf:type owl:Restriction ;
                                                                                                             owl:onProperty <http://www.semanticweb.org/94180/ontologies/2023/3/untitled-ontology-8/requiredParameters> ;
                                                                                                             owl:someValuesFrom <http://www.semanticweb.org/94180/ontologies/2023/3/untitled-ontology-8/Cohesion>
                                                                                                           ] ,
                                                                                                           [ rdf:type owl:Restriction ;
                                                                                                             owl:onProperty <http://www.semanticweb.org/94180/ontologies/2023/3/untitled-ontology-8/requiredParameters> ;
                                                                                                             owl:someValuesFrom <http://www.semanticweb.org/94180/ontologies/2023/3/untitled-ontology-8/Internal_friction_angle>
                                                                                                           ] ,
                                                                                                           [ rdf:type owl:Restriction ;
                                                                                                             owl:onProperty <http://www.semanticweb.org/94180/ontologies/2023/3/untitled-ontology-8/requiredParameters> ;
                                                                                                             owl:someValuesFrom <http://www.semanticweb.org/94180/ontologies/2023/3/untitled-ontology-8/Material_parameters>
                                                                                                           ] ,
                                                                                                           [ rdf:type owl:Restriction ;
                                                                                                             owl:onProperty <http://www.semanticweb.org/94180/ontologies/2023/3/untitled-ontology-8/requiredParameters> ;
                                                                                                             owl:someValuesFrom <http://www.semanticweb.org/94180/ontologies/2023/3/untitled-ontology-8/Permeability>
                                                                                                           ] ,
                                                                                                           [ rdf:type owl:Restriction ;
                                                                                                             owl:onProperty <http://www.semanticweb.org/94180/ontologies/2023/3/untitled-ontology-8/requiredParameters> ;
                                                                                                             owl:someValuesFrom <http://www.semanticweb.org/94180/ontologies/2023/3/untitled-ontology-8/Permeability_coefficient>
                                                                                                           ] ,
                                                                                                           [ rdf:type owl:Restriction ;
                                                                                                             owl:onProperty <http://www.semanticweb.org/94180/ontologies/2023/3/untitled-ontology-8/requiredParameters> ;
                                                                                                             owl:someValuesFrom <http://www.semanticweb.org/94180/ontologies/2023/3/untitled-ontology-8/Shear_modulus>
                                                                                                           ] ,
                                                                                                           [ rdf:type owl:Restriction ;
                                                                                                             owl:onProperty <http://www.semanticweb.org/94180/ontologies/2023/3/untitled-ontology-8/requiredParameters> ;
                                                                                                             owl:someValuesFrom <http://www.semanticweb.org/94180/ontologies/2023/3/untitled-ontology-8/Shear_strength>
                                                                                                           ] ;
                                                                                           <http://www.semanticweb.org/94180/ontologies/2023/3/untitled-ontology-8/comment> "Wind tunnel models can be used to simulate the effects of wind on side slopes, especially in terrain such as viaducts or cliffs. By simulating the wind flow in the model, the effect of wind on slope stability can be studied." ;
                                                                                           <http://www.semanticweb.org/94180/ontologies/2023/3/untitled-ontology-8/principle_of_the_model> """1. Simulate terrain and structures: The wind tunnel model needs to select the appropriate terrain and structures for simulation according to the actual situation. For landslide studies, slopes of different terrain can be simulated, as well as vegetation, rocks, or soils that may be affected by wind. In addition, buildings or other man-made structures can be simulated to study the effects of wind on these structures.
2. Simulate the wind field: In the wind tunnel model, the wind field with different wind speeds and directions is simulated by controlling a fan or other device. By adjusting the wind speed and direction, the effect of wind under different meteorological conditions on the terrain and structure can be simulated, including changes in wind speed and direction.
3. Measurement and analysis: Sensors and measuring equipment are installed during the experiment to monitor the effects of wind on the terrain and structure. These devices can record surface wind speed, pressure distribution, structural vibrations, and other parameters, thus helping researchers analyze the mechanism of wind action.
4. Data analysis and application: Through the analysis of experimental data, we can understand the influence of wind on the terrain and structure, including the movement of wind on surface particles, the distortion and deformation of vegetation, and the force of buildings. These data can provide a scientific basis for relevant engineering design and disaster prevention and mitigation.""" .


